lead_paragraph: Aliaksandra Sasnovich produced the biggest upset of the Pan Pacific Open on Thursday, ousting third-seeded Karolina Pliskova in straight sets to advance to the quarterfinals.

headline.print_headline: Sasnovich Upsets 3rd Seed Pliskova at Pan Pacific Open
